init_text: Humans once wielded formidable magical power. But with over 7 billion of us on the planet now, Mana has spread far too thinly to have any effect. When hostile aliens reduce humanity to a mere fraction, the survivors discover an old power has begun to reawaken once again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Unusual gems and magical talismans are appearing all over the world.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They're called "Shards" and those who have them can draw upon the vast stores of magic energy they contain.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: As more and more of these Shards are found, the magic within them is being used to resurrect a world that was lost during the great war.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But magical power comes with a price.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Every Shard has a human host, and as the power of magic works to recreate the world as it once was, these hosts begin to die...

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: A young man named Asher is drawn to a mysterious Shard that is accompanied by an ethereal woman.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He is the latest in a long line of hosts and he is about to discover his true purpose.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Asher's destiny is to protect every Shard and their hosts, as well as serve as one of the last links between our world and

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: the magical one that has been lost for so long.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Now he must learn to master his powers, and lead humanity into a new age of magic.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: If he fails, he will die.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: If he succeeds, the world will be reborn.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They are trying to do good, by their own twisted standard.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The aliens are not all bad, but the humans are not all good.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: With so much magic now available to the humans, this will be a time of great change for Earth.
